Simon Says bundles / downloads and drives two third-party tools at runtime:
  • yt-dlp  — Unlicense (public domain).  https://github.com/yt-dlp/yt-dlp
  • ffmpeg  — LGPL/GPL depending on build. https://ffmpeg.org
These retain their own licenses; Simon Says invokes them as external programs.
